The Alex Jones Show

Tuesday January 05, 2009.

Mike Rivero will be live via webcam for Prison Planet TV subscribers.  Alex also talks with Constitutional scholar Dr. Edwin Vieira about the militarization of law enforcement and Candadian economist and author Michel Chossudovsky about the situation in Gaza.  Alex also discusses the issues of the day and takes your calls.

Hour-1: News

Hour-2: Mike Rivero discusses discusses Obama's socialist agenda and thinks we need more even socialism to correct the problems!

Hour-3: Dr. Edwin Vieira discusses the police state and the Constitutional Militia

Hour-4: Dr. Michel Chossudovsky on Israel's invasion of Gaza and the economic collapse
